string.name: desc
string.value: This gem gives your pet the ability to automatically cast buff skills onto its owner. Place your desired skill in the open slot next to the Auto Buff Gem in the pet's Equipment Inventory. You no longer have to worry about casting your favorite buff, your pet will do it for you!
